@@TJvEasterEgg
Description:
This component is for fun only ... Put it in an about box and specify the string you want to be the egg ... And when the string has been entered by the user, you receive an event and you have to show the egg. (An easter egg is a form or a funny feature hided from common users, in delphi, in the about box, try alt+developers or alt+team and alt+jedi (in delphi5)).

